==Soundtrack==
The music of the film was composed and lyrics were written by [[Hamsalekha]].<ref>[http://kannada-newmp3.blogspot.in/2009/11/rana-ranga.html Ranaranga songs]</ref> Actor [[Rajkumar (actor)|Rajkumar]] recorded the song "Jagave Ondu Ranaranga".

